 H  1.01  H.blyp-hgh.UPF
 O  16.0  O.blyp-hgh.UPF
ATOMIC_POSITIONS bohr
 O 0.003370 -0.002286 0.122203
 H -0.009505 0.786701 -0.472413
 H -0.043888 -0.750490 -0.528277
K_POINTS
 1
0.0 0.0 0.0 1.0